16:12.818 --> 16:14.785
But he's not torturing animals.

16:14.887 --> 16:17.087
You're right. How are we so blessed?

16:25.264 --> 16:28.165
Look. He already made friends.

16:28.267 --> 16:30.067
Yeah. Pig friends.

16:30.169 --> 16:31.468
