Aren't <i> you</i> going to say goodbye?

18:06.198 --> 18:08.432
Fine.

18:10.069 --> 18:11.935
Hey.

18:12.038 --> 18:14.304
Take it easy, pig.

18:14.407 --> 18:17.775
Oliver, you're never
going to see him again.

18:17.877 --> 18:20.778
Okay.

18:22.715 --> 18:24.782
I guess she's right.

18:24.850 --> 18:27.051
I'm not gonna see you again.

18:29.955 --> 18:31.855
But that's life.

18:36.762 --> 18:38.629
I just want you to know...

18:40.433 --> 18:42.700
...meeting you was one
of the best things

18:42.768 --> 18:44.134
that's ever happened to me.

18:44.236 --> 18:46.036
I'm sorry I never told you that.

18:46.105 --> 18:48.772
I'm just...

18:50.009 --> 18:52.443
The thing is,

18:52.545 --> 18:55.212
I feel like I just got to know you,

18:55.281 --> 18:56.914
