18:58.984 --> 19:00.451
It's not fair!

19:02.588 --> 19:04.354
I know, baby.

19:04.457 --> 19:05.422
I know.

19:07.393 --> 19:10.994
Oh, my sweet boy.

19:25.644 --> 19:27.978
It was a good idea to play
Monopoly in honor of Spencer.

19:28.047 --> 19:30.214
Yeah, we would've caught him
sneaking money into his pocket,

19:30.316 --> 19:31.982
